  &lt;li&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/spring-projects/spring-boot/issues/13834&quot; class=&quot;external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt;提供一致的方法来发现主要DispatcherServlet的路径&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/li&gt; 
  &lt;li&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/spring-projects/spring-boot/issues/13900&quot; class=&quot;external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt;项目特定设置未在Eclipse中应用&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/li&gt; 
  &lt;li&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/spring-projects/spring-boot/issues/13636&quot; class=&quot;external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt;由于缺少默认构造函数而无法绑定的属性很难诊断&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/li&gt; 
  &lt;li&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/spring-projects/spring-boot/issues/13155&quot; class=&quot;external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt;在使用JdbcTemplate之前，数据库迁移可能尚未运行&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/li&gt; 
  &lt;li&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/spring-projects/spring-boot/issues/13508&quot; class=&quot;external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt;RedisCacheConfiguration缺少@ConditionalOnClass检查&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/li&gt; 
